{"tid":652474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美女教練勾上已婚富商　下體全裸遭活逮","createTime":"2018-05-04T00:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T08:13:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00fc4262728d47fa2521d4459ed6168a0860102a","tid":652474,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:50:29.000Z","msg":"抓姦在床，不認都不行！<br />\n<br />\n今日出刊的《自由時報》報導，年近7旬的陳姓富商3年前到某五星級飯店游泳，認識30歲身材健美的美女游泳教練小芬(化名)，兩人發展出不倫戀，多次出遊、偷情。<br />\n<br />\n陳男妻子事後由閨密口中得知兩人事情，氣得找徵信社跟監、蒐證，2016年2月某日深夜，在徵信社陪同下，陳妻前往小芬住處抓姦，一衝進房間就拿起相機拍照蒐證，此刻全身赤裸的小芬嚇得從床上跳起來躲在床角，陳男見狀丟一件浴衣給她遮掩，但光溜溜的臀部已被拍得一清二楚。<br />\n<br />\n陳妻事後提告小芬通姦罪、並求償500萬元。抓姦照片加上用的保險套成鐵證，法官依通姦罪判小芬4月徒刑定讞、高等法院昨再判她需賠償陳妻60萬元。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180504/640_0f32bf503c2643535639ed31223dae90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180504%2F640_0f32bf503c2643535639ed31223dae90.jpg&h=61eff43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180504/1347031/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180504%2F1347031%2F&d=UJQ0sf2IZtaF7nkEhBWyPwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ce40e542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180504%2F1347031%2F&h=6e87b63f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180504/1347031/</a>"},{"pid":"8c90357b6c47b3a01883127659c964131540abae","tid":652474,"uid":97708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:53:56.000Z","msg":"moto"},{"pid":"57cf1aa20c4ce49c87af272091703d672999cc30","tid":652474,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:14:25.000Z","msg":"點証明係美女勾富商, 而唔係富商勾美女呀 ?"},{"pid":"91edfe07ec37f6c2290ed06b8150eaebf263df60","tid":652474,"uid":139150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"57c